    public class LceRetrofitPresenter<V extends MvpLceView<M>,M>
extends MvpBasePresenter<V>
    A Presenter that can be used with MvpLceView and Retrofit. It provides LceRetrofitPresenter.LceCallback that can be used as Callback for retrofit requests.
